---
title: Speedy Chermoula Beef Bulgur Bowl with Apricots, Spinach and Yoghurt
description: Perfect for a midweek meal, this Speedy Chermoula Beef Bulgur Bowl can be on your table in less than 25 minutes. Chermoula spice mix is widely used in North African cuisine, fragrant with paprika, turmeric and coriander.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R15_W41_UK_R17580-4_Main_low-ee2beb22.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66b22e32a1293bffe8e018cb-en-GB.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: Middle Eastern
